summary: Adds sunrays to the game with the ENB Series Mod
descriptionHtml:
DESCRIPTION


This mod is a simple tweak of the ENB preset who adds ONLY sunrays to your game.
New version 1.1 for better performances.

-Use the ENBSeries v0.113

-No performance hit noticed, on my pc at least. 


INSTALLATION:

-You need to download the ENBSeries v0.113 by Boris Vorontso. 
Here http://www.enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0113.htm   

-Place ONLY the   d3d9.dll from the\"WrapperVersion\" folder  file in your Skyrim root folder.

-Just place all the content from my file to your Skyrim root folder.
author: Clemtout
